query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS pixel_sessions (
  id BIGINT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  sessionId VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  pixelUserId VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,
  artistId INT,
  startedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  endedAt TIMESTAMP NULL,
  durationSeconds INT,
  pageViews INT DEFAULT 0,
  events INT DEFAULT 0,
  converted TINYINT DEFAULT 0,
  revenue DECIMAL(10,2) DEFAULT 0.00,
  landingPage TEXT,
  exitPage TEXT,
  referrer TEXT,
  utmSource VARCHAR(100),
  utmMedium VARCHAR(100),
  utmCampaign VARCHAR(100),
  country VARCHAR(2),
  deviceType VARCHAR(20),
  INDEX pixel_user_idx (pixelUserId),
  INDEX artist_idx (artistId),
  INDEX started_at_idx (startedAt),
  INDEX converted_idx (converted)
);
